To run the Zookeeper service -- > bin/zookeeper-server-start.sh config/zookeeper.properties
To run the kafka server --> bin/kafka-server-start.sh config/server.properties
To create the topic --> bin/kafka-topics.sh --bootstrap-server localhost:9092 --topic first_topic --create --partition 3 --replication-factor 1
To check the messages from the listener -- > bin/kafka-console-consumer.sh --topic nikhilTopic --from-beginning --bootstrap-server localhost:9092